me.taylorkelly.mywarp.warp

Interface Warp

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Warp>

    public interface Warp
extends java.lang.Comparable<Warp>
    Represents a Warp. Implementations must ensure that two Warps are equal if, and only if their names are equal.

    To create a Warp use the WarpBuilder.

      • getPopularityScore

        double getPopularityScore()
        Gets this Warp's popularity score. The score is influenced by the number of visits a Warp received since it was created, while newer Warps receive a better score than older Warps.

        the popularity score of this Warp
